name: The Celebration
description:
Inspires me to continue to be grateful for the blessings You have given me and my parents and to do something.

I prostrate my face to the one who created it, form its appearance, and open its hearing and sight
Indeed.

I have placed myself on the earth and We have prepared for you on the earth (source) of livelihood. You are very little grateful.


Artwork by RAKASU
